<br>
Drink orange juice.  I know some people go for the overdose on vitamin C, but I find natural sources of vitamins work best.<br>
<br>
Swimming and saunas.  Excess fluid can be a pain if you suffer from this condition. This combination helps you avoid too much fluid inside.<br>
<br>
The right keyboard tray. Spent 300 dollars both at work and at home getting a tray for my keyboard which adjusts properly. I also now use a trackball for both.<br>
